<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>British Policy towards Princely States</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>1. Policy of Ring Fencing (1765-1813)</p>
<p>- Subsidiary alliance by Wellesley&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. Policy of Subordinate Isolation (1813-1857)</p>
<p>- Paramountcy</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>3. Policy of Subordinate Union (1857-1935)</p>
<p>- Paramountcy supremacy of crown&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>4. Policy of Equal Federation (1935-1947)</p>
<p>- Federal Assembly by Government of India Act, 1935</p>